@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mvocig(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (0.27 + ((v2 + 0.14 * tmp + 0.63) / (v0 + 0.83 - v1 + 0.13)))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.abs(0.13))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.exp((v0 + 0.31 / tmp + 0.90)))
    v0 = (0.20 - 0.55)
    v2 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
